comments:
Alien words had letters that were unfamiliar to me.
I first tried to learn the first 2-3 letters to identify the item, but it was very overwhelming for me, then I switched to trying to learn the last letter of each word before the last #.
Task was very hard due to the fact that we barely have time to process information and we get many pieces in a row.
Second part was definitively easier than the first.

Moreover, I don't think I even got to learn a full word, not even half of one.
